♻️ E-Waste Management System
🚀 Overview

The E-Waste Management System is a smart and eco-friendly solution designed to manage electronic waste efficiently. This project integrates AI, real-time data fetching, and secure data wiping protocols to ensure both environmental safety and user data privacy. It enables users to identify e-waste, locate nearby recycling centers, and dispose of devices responsibly.

🔥 Key Features
📷 AI-Based Camera Scanner
Real-time image scanning using camera
Detects e-waste items such as mobiles, batteries, and laptops
Provides instant classification
🌐 Real-Time Data Fetch
Retrieves nearby authorized e-waste recycling centers
Displays location, distance, and navigation details
Uses live API data instead of static information
🔐 Secure Data Wiping System

Ensures complete removal of personal data before recycling:

🟡 Before Wiping
Backup important data
Logout from accounts
Remove SIM/SD cards
🔵 During Wiping
Secure data deletion using:
DoD 5220.22-M standard
NIST 800-88 guidelines
Multiple overwrite passes
Real-time progress tracking
🟢 After Wiping
Verification of complete data removal
Confirmation status display
Optional data erasure certification
📍 Nearby Recycling Centers
Locate e-waste collection centers using maps
Access directions and contact details
🚚 Pickup Request System
Schedule doorstep pickup for e-waste
Select preferred date and time
📊 User Dashboard
Track total e-waste recycled
View environmental impact (CO₂ saved)
🎁 Reward System
Earn points for responsible recycling
Redeem rewards and incentives
💻 Tech Stack
Mobile App: Flutter
Web App: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend (Optional): Node.js / Firebase
APIs: Google Maps API
AI Model (Optional): TensorFlow / Teachable Machine
